# STANDARDS

## Purpose

Governed architecture standards and reusable patterns for `<enterprise-id>`.

## Ownership

Owner: `<standards-owner>`

Repository instructions are defined by the root `AGENTS.md`.

## Pattern Index

Default machine-readable index: [pattern-index.yml](<pattern-index-ref>)

